metadata.name: Bonded by Black Roses
metadata.description:
The true love we share can never be broken 
As time feels like its standing still, its continuously moving forward. The bonds we make throughout that time and places encountered together can never be severed with the person you share those moments with. A lovers bond is strong beyond measure and here after moving on from this plane of existence a lover bond bound by something magical gives an opportunity for ravens to carry the spirits to return and spend another magical moment together being "Bonded by Black Roses"

Black roses is a series i'm doing 
Thank you for taking this journey with me
